room_title: Escape room "Guards Vs Prisoners" by The Great Xscape Room in Virginia Beach
room_address: 2548 Virginia Beach Blvd Ste 106, Virginia Beach VA 23452
room_description: Welcome to the VB Pen! Xscapes from prisons are at an all-time high. A prisoner has Xscaped and has caused all the doors to be secured. You and the other guards OR you and your cellmates hatch a plan to Xscape and lock up the counterpart group. Pick your side. May the best guard or prisoner win!
